May which thou cam<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="3 letters">,</HI> or that may only imply <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> meeting him in the Way&mdash;It is <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">ch Matter&mdash;It is plain Chri&s;t here &s;peaks <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> him, and &s;ays, <HI>I am Je&s;us whom thou per&s;e|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="4 letters"></HI>&mdash;It is remarkable, how our Lord takes <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 span"> the Name of <HI>Je&s;us</HI>&mdash;For it is a Name <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> when he delights&mdash;I am <HI>Je&s;us,</HI> a <HI>Saviour of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> People,</HI> both from the Guilt and Power of th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="2 letters">r Sin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">&punc;&mdash;But a <HI>Je&s;us whom thou per&s;ecute&s;t</HI>&mdash;This &s;eem<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter"> to be &s;poken to convince <HI>Saul</HI> more and more of his Sin, and I doubt <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> but every Word was &s;harper than a two edged Sword, and came like &s;o many Daggers to his Heart&mdash;Oh, how did the&s;e Words affect him <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> a <HI>Je&s;us!</HI> a <HI>Saviour!</HI> and yet I am per&s;ecuting him! This &s;trikes him with Horror&mdash;But then the Word <HI>Je&s;us,</HI> tho' <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 letter">e was a Per&s;ecutor, might give him &s;ome Hope&mdash;However, our dear Lord, to con|vince <HI>Saul</HI> that he was to be &s;aved by Grace, and that <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="AELD" EXTENT="1 word"> was not afraid of his Power and En|mity, tells him&mdash;<HI>"It is hard for thee to kick again&s;t the Pricks"</HI>&mdash;As much as to &s;ay, tho' he was per&s;ecuting